WEBVTT

00:00:09.655 --> 00:00:14.410 line:90% position:50% align:center
Another year has gone by.

00:00:14.410 --> 00:00:19.915 line:90% position:50% align:center
Are you ready?
’Cause it’s convention time!

00:00:19.915 --> 00:00:25.337 line:90% position:50% align:center
I’ve got my bag,
Love in my heart.

00:00:25.337 --> 00:00:30.009 line:90% position:50% align:center
Can’t wait to be there
Before the music starts.

00:00:30.009 --> 00:00:34.847 line:90% position:50% align:center
It’s convention time!

00:00:34.847 --> 00:00:44.899 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together in Jehovah’s house,
There’s no better place to be—

00:00:44.899 --> 00:00:55.492 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together in Jehovah’s house
With my worldwide family.

00:00:55.492 --> 00:01:01.081 line:90% position:50% align:center
We could be friends,
Don’t you agree?

00:01:01.081 --> 00:01:06.170 line:90% position:50% align:center
Why don’t you take a seat
right next to me?

00:01:06.170 --> 00:01:11.508 line:90% position:50% align:center
We’re taking notes
And singing songs.

00:01:11.508 --> 00:01:16.013 line:90% position:50% align:center
We have the same hope—
That’s why we get along!

00:01:16.013 --> 00:01:20.768 line:90% position:50% align:center
It’s convention time!

00:01:20.768 --> 00:01:30.903 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together in Jehovah’s house,
There’s no better place to be—

00:01:30.903 --> 00:01:41.121 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together in Jehovah’s house
With our worldwide family.

00:01:41.121 --> 00:01:51.840 line:90% position:50% align:center
Together in Jehovah’s house,
There’s no better place to be.

00:01:51.840 --> 00:01:57.346 line:90% position:50% align:center
And we can play a part
in filling ev’ry heart

00:01:57.346 --> 00:02:07.940 line:90% position:50% align:center
In this worldwide family.

